<item>
            <title>[LU-3336] LFSCK II: MDT-OST OST orphan handling</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3336</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This ticket relates to handling of OST orphan cleanup.  This includes:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;create an in-memory bitmap for OST FIDs that have been referenced during MDS Pass 1 checking&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;after the OST Pass 2 scanning is complete, any OST objects that have not been referenced need to be verified with the MDT, and added to &lt;tt&gt;lost+found&lt;/tt&gt; or unlinked (depending on administrator preference)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
